header_to_src.sh [-h] header_path dir_src... -- program to put licence header to src/headers files

where:
	-h			Show this help text
	header_path	Path of the licence header
	dir_src		Directory where sources/headers are

Execute header_to_src.sh to src files (.cpp/.h/.c/.hpp/.sh) placed in directories passed as argument.

It will add a licence header at the beginning of the source code.

WARNING : The program doesn't check if a header is already present in source files.
